{"tid":1070529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨：兩度請辭港鐵主席但被政府挽留","createTime":"2019-03-20T17:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T04:31:40.000Z","uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50a56518d44a22f03cd7bf81a93d09cff10004c9","tid":1070529,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"港鐵就沙中綫提交予政府的報告有不準確，港鐵主席馬時亨表示，有此情況是不能接受，董事局亦蒙在鼓裡，未能適時收到準確及全面的資料，對此感到非常失望和遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨說，自己曾兩度向行政長官林鄭月娥請辭，但政府希望他留下，處理行政總裁招聘及沙中綫遺留的問題。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨強調，很尊重問責精神，留下是因為自己是有責任感的人，而他的主席合約並沒有約滿酬金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411124-20180807.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411124-20180807.htm&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV6T%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=c5481fbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411124-20180807.htm&h=f2b2e560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411124-20180807.htm</a>"},{"pid":"96d4fc53dfc22f6e40f1231398f8147fba5e6149","tid":1070529,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"即係本身唔使請辭 都合約滿?"},{"pid":"05466b41d5f7c89240fb64aed8734103a7c7a3cb","tid":1070529,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢條友真係廢到核爆"},{"pid":"93b388506997b5a01aeaddbd3d66faa58dabcc5b","tid":1070529,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"2018-08-07 HKT 18:23"},{"pid":"4b8275a9e899f2eacb5b687dfdd8f5f16ee11592","tid":1070529,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b388506997b5a01aeaddbd3d66faa58dabcc5b","tid":1070529,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"2018-08-07 HKT 18:23"},"cite